item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: sample-data
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

Our Directors

Their Vision

Add your own custom background colors and images to your pages. Each page section within a One Pager and all separate pages can have their own unique background style. And if thats not enough, you can also use Full Width Sections to add even more variations.

Eco-Friendly Minded

item.title: Services
item.dc:creator: sample-data
item.content:encoded:
[one_third] [icon_box title="100% Responsive" icon="mobile-phone"] Every element within RAW has been designed to be fully responsive on all devices. This means that when you build a website using RAW it can be displayed on desktops, laptops, tablets and mobile phones. If you want to see this in action just resize your browser. [/icon_box] [/one_third] [one_third] [icon_box title="Advanced Admin Panel" icon="cog"] With the Advanced Admin Panel, you will be able to change pretty much anything you like, such as colors, fonts, header layout. The Theme Options include a Setup Guide, which helps you to setup your theme. Choose one of our presets and personalize the appearance for your website. [/icon_box] [/one_third] [one_third_last] [icon_box title="Retina Ready" icon="eye-open"] Every aspect of the design is fully optimized for retina and other high density screens. This results in an absolutely fabulous look on MacBooks Pro Retina, iPads, iPhones and other high density resolution screens. In the Theme Options you can upload your retina logo's, so that these will look ultra sharp too. [/icon_box] [/one_third_last]
[spacer height="40"]
[one_third] [icon_box title="Header Options" icon="tasks"] Customize the look and feel of the header the way you like. You can change it's colors, fonts, enable or disable the Call to Action Button. Optionally add an additional bar for multi language options, 2 extra menus, social media icons. [/icon_box] [/one_third] [one_third] [icon_box title="70+ Shortcodes" icon="reorder"] With over 70 shortcodes you will have no trouble building any layout, with any look you like. We have included all popular shortcodes such as: Accordions, Toggles, Tabs, Buttons, Pricing Tables, Progress Bars, Callout Boxes, Icons, Testimonials, etc. Just have a look at the list of shortcodes to see what the possibilities are. [/icon_box] [/one_third]
[one_third_last] [icon_box title="Suitable for Landing Pages" icon="signin"] With RAW you can create as many One Pagers as you like. Interconnect them and use a multi page structure to build your main website. Each One Pager can have it's own Call to Action Buttons and Pop-Ups. With the Gravity Forms integration you can easily build your custom forms and manage your leads. [/icon_box] [/one_third_last]

item.title: Pricing
item.dc:creator: sample-data
item.content:encoded:
[one_third] [icon_box title="Slider Revolution" icon="refresh" icon_style="alt"] This theme comes equipped with Slider Revolution. With Revolution Slider you can choose from a tons of unique transition effect, pre-load your images, embed video's, auto stop on user interaction, setup your own styles and effects. We have included this $17 premium slider for Free. [/icon_box] [spacer height="20"] [icon_box title="LayerSlider Integrated" icon="stack-3" icon_type="icomoon" icon_style="alt"] Besides Slider Revolution, this theme also comes equipped with Layer Slider integration and has been included for Free. This means you will not have to go and buy Layer Slider separately for $17. Simply tell RAW that you want to use it and it will be available for use. [/icon_box] [spacer height="20"] [icon_box title="$118 Free Plugin Value" icon="puzzle" icon_type="icomoon" icon_style="alt"] RAW includes the 2 most popular sliders around: Slider Revolution and LayerSlider. It also includes IsoTope and IcoMoon Ultimate Premium Icons. This totals to $118 of Plugin Value which you will get for Free when you purchase this template.
